[{"id":"VH978973","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><include href=\"../Passage/VH978968.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Incineration is one solution to reduce the volume of municipal solid waste. Municipal solid waste can be used to produce energy at waste-to-energy plants. Based on the data in the graphs, which of the following materials would be best suited for incineration to reduce total volume, produce energy, and have minimal release of air pollutants?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH978973_rubric","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<div class=\"stimulus_reference\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\">\n<div class=\"passage\">\n<div class=\"prose style:1\">\n<p class=\"passage_para\">The two pie charts show municipal solid waste (<span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"M S W\"><math alttext=\"M S W\" overflow=\"scroll\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>MSW</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>) in the United States, 2015.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure presents two pie charts. The first pie chart is titled, Total M S W Generation in the United States by type of waste, 2015. A note indicates that the total equals 262 million tons. The data represented in the circle graph are as follows. Food Waste, 15.1%; Plastics, 13.1%; Metals, 9.1 %; Rubber, Leather, and Textiles, 9.3%; Wood, 6.2%; Glass, 4.4%; Other, 3.6%; Paper, 25.9%; Yard Trimmings, 13.3%. The second pie chart titled, Management of M S W in the United States, 2015. A note indicates that the total equals 262 million tons. The data represented in the circle graph are as follows. Recycling, 25.8%; Combustion with Energy Recovery, 12.8%; Composting, 8.9%; and Landfilled, 52.5%.\" height=\"286\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH978968.g05.png\" width=\"550\" /></div>\n</div>\n"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Glass</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Wood</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Metals</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Plastics</p>"],"answer":1}]